The paper discusses the challenges and failures of human-machine teaming, which involves human-computer interaction (cs.HC), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), robotics (cs.RO), and systems and control (cs.SY). The paper also proposes a mathematical theory for improving HMTs, which involves machine learning (cs.LG).
